						               													<description>The shrewd elf Remigius has taken control of the family castle, in which great-great aunt Mathilda once lived. If you want to recapture the castle, you have to catch Remigius by Christmas! The imp is hiding somewhere in one of the many rooms. But be careful: only one room may be entered each day. If you manage to solve the riddle of the respective room, you will find out in which room you can look for the imp on the next day. Clever combination skills, imagination and creativity are required now! But don't worry, if things get stuck, there is a table on the back of the pack with 2 tips for each puzzle and a breakdown of the solution. Now you have to combine cleverly to save the castle and bring it back into the family's possession within 24 days! Let's go, time is running.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Ravensburger joins in with Exit Room Advent Calendars. Advent season will be exciting as an escape room. Each of the 24 virtual rooms - one for each day of Advent season - will offer a thrilling riddle. Solving it will lead on to the next room and step by step you will recapture what belongs to you and your family.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
